query:
SELECT gm.id, gm.groupId, gm.userId, gm.latitude, gm.longitude, gm.isRiding, gm.lastLocationUpdate, u.name 
FROM group_members gm 
LEFT JOIN users u ON gm.userId = u.id 
ORDER BY gm.lastLocationUpdate DESC 
LIMIT 20;
